title: Episode 86: Ft. Keyshia Cole
itunes:title: Episode 86: Ft. Keyshia Cole
description:
This week we are popping Keyshia Cole's Lip Service cherry and you know the ladies are not holding anything back! Find out about that one time a man asked Keyshia to buy him sneakers, how she is handling being 8 months celibate while aiming to go a whole year, why she thinks all men cheat and not considering herself a freak. Listen as Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Lore'l get into how far you should let an "investigation" go before you confront a cheater, what to do when the other woman calls you, ass licking
